                                <note>Top left corner, National Library book label with current signum; top of page in dark ink by a contemporary hand: <quote>Liber Magistri Mathei de brawnsbergk Anno 1466 In quo continentur subscripta Et primo novem libri </quote> and a table of contents.</note>
